                        <div>
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-success)]">STRENGTHS</span>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-1 text-slate-300 space-y-1">
                                <li>**Deepest Gov't Penetration:** Trusted relationships across **all US Intelligence and Defense agencies**.</li>
                                <li>**Tech Leadership:** Recognized lead in mission-critical **Cybersecurity and AI/Data Science** solutions.</li>
                                <li>**Cleared Talent:** Superior reputation for highly-cleared personnel (**TS/SCI**).</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-warning)]">WEAKNESSES</span>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 mt-1 text-slate-300 space-y-1">
                                <li>**Revenue Concentration:** Extreme reliance on the **U.S. Federal Government** (~97%), heightening budget sensitivity.</li>
                                <li>**Legacy Perception:** Ongoing effort to shed the "consulting" legacy to fully compete as a technology integrator.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="bg-slate-700 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-xl">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-300">Competitive Comparison</h3>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <p class="text-slate-300">
                            The competitive landscape is dominated by large integrators, each with a slightly different focus:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside ml-4 space-y-2 text-slate-300">
                            <li>**Leidos:** Greater scale in large IT infrastructure and hardware integration; often manages higher-value, non-services-only contracts.</li>
                            <li>**CACI:** Highly specialized in rapid delivery of proprietary technology and products, particularly in the Intelligence community.</li>
                            <li>**SAIC:** Stronger presence in large-scale logistics and platform integration services, offering diversification outside of core strategic consulting.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="text-sm italic text-slate-400 pt-2 border-t border-slate-600">
                            All competitors face intense wage inflation and recruiting challenges for top-tier cleared technical talent.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
